{"article_id":"pvSJRKAzeU6SCraN","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"The Renaissance Hotel","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"- the official hotel","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"for March for Life participants","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"to gather in Washington , D.C. -","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"was buzzing with excitement Thursday .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Thousands of people were meeting for events ahead of Friday ' s anti-abortion March for Life .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"It ' s the 44th year of the march ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"but this time ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"many attendees said ,","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"is the first in nearly a decade","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"they feel","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"their voices will be heard -","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"and that 's because of President Trump and Vice President Pence .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"\" With the administration","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"that has promised pro-life policies","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"being enacted","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"there ' s just a lot of hope and a lot of enthusiasm , \"","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Jeanne Mancini , president of the March for Life , told .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"\" It sure does , \" feel different under Trump than previous marches","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"when Barack Obama was president ,","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"Mancini said .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Obama was a supporter of abortion rights","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"and threatened to veto any legislation","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"that would curb them .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"\" We ' ve seen one executive order after the other","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"really not protecting the inherent dignity of the human person from conception to natural death .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"It ' s a breath of relief , a breath fresh air , for us to now have people","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"who are wanting to forward pro-life policies , \"","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"Mancini continued .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"The new administration has made clear","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"that they are anti-abortion .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"One of the first executive orders","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"Trump signed","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"was to prohibit U.S. aid from going to international organizations","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"that promote abortion .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"Trump has also repeatedly vowed","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"that whomever","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"he chooses to fill the vacant position on the Supreme Court","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"will be pro-life .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"And or the first time in the march 's history , the vice president will speak .","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"Pence announced Thursday","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"he 'd be speaking ;","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"senior adviser Kellyanne Conway is set to address the crowd as well .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"\" I think","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Trump ' s made it very clear","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"that he ' s somebody","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"who considers himself pro-life ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"even if he didn ' t always , \"","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"Ashley McGuire , a senior fellow with the Catholic Association , told .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"\" By signing the Mexico City executive order ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"you know","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"having that be one of the first things","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"his administration did ,","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"was another very strong signal to the pro-life community","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"that he intends to make good on what he said to us on those issues , \"","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"she said .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"\" I think","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"that pro-lifers feel like","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"maybe we have a voice at the federal level","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"-","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"there ' s that hope","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"that we will have that voice .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Before , there was no hope , \"","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"said Abby Johnson , founder of And Then There Were None ,","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"which is an organization","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"that works","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"to get workers out of abortion-related jobs .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Before she became an anti-abortion activist ,","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"Johnson was a Planned Parenthood clinic director .","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"Trump wields his presidential pen ,","depth":4},{"id":71,"text":"signing memos on trade , hiring , abortion","depth":4},{"id":72,"text":"The march will begin with an hourlong rally at the Washington Monument , with several Republican lawmakers on the schedule .","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"Following the rally ,","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"marchers will walk the roughly two miles between the monument to the Supreme Court and U.S. Capitol .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"Then marchers will move to the House and Senate buildings","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"to visit their lawmakers .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"Trump said in an interview with ABC","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"that aired Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"he \" was told you will have a very large crowd of people '' at the March for Life .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"`` I don ' t know","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"as large or larger ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"some people said","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"it ' s gon na be larger \" than last week ' s Women ' s March ,","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"Trump said .","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"Last weekend , huge crowds gathered in cities around the world for the first-ever Women ' s March ,","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"which was organized in response to Trump ' s election .","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"While people marched for a whole slew of reasons","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"- equal pay , climate change , racial equality , LGBT equality , among them -","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"many attendees were there","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"to support Planned Parenthood and abortion rights .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"In Washington alone , there were an estimated 500,000 marchers .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"One anti-abortion group told","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"that he was rejected from cosponsoring the event","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"after the Women ' s March announced","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"it supported abortion rights .","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"The march organizers could not be reached","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"to confirm the account .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":195,"left":0,"right":194,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":194,"left":166,"right":193,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":136,"right":165,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":126,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":103,"right":125,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":102,"right":6,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":101,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":101,"left":1,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":2,"right":99,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":109,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":108,"right":13,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":7,"right":107,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":107,"left":104,"right":106,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":104,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"pa